      "heading": "Documentation Protocol",
      "level": 2,
      "slug": "documentation-protocol",
      "prose": "1. **JSON First**: Define routes and metadata in `*_page.json`.\n2. **Standardize**: Run `python json_to_markdown.py` to generate page specs.\n3. **Audit**: Apply [DESIGN_SYMBOLS.md](pages/DESIGN_SYMBOLS.md) and standardized **Navigation** handoffs.\n4. **Link**: Run `python link_endpoint_specs.py` to bind UI to GraphQL contracts.\n5. **Augment**: Run `augment_page_specs.py` for global parity.",
      "tables": [],
      "lists": [
        {
          "ordered": false,
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "**JSON First**: Define routes and metadata in `*_page.json`.",
